n\">🕶️<\/span>\n        <h3>100% UNDETECTABLE<\/h3>\n        <p>Looks like real hair. No one will ever know.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- Center image -->\n    <div class=\"rizen-features__center\">\n      <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0957\/2981\/1738\/files\/07dcc0186d4545df8542924db385cb12-ezgif.com-optimize.webp?v=1774812263\" \/>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <!-- Right column -->\n    <div class=\"rizen-features__col\">\n      <div class=\"rizen-features__item\">\n        <span class=\"rizen-features__icon\">🎯<\/span>\n        <h3>TARGETED PRECISION<\/h3>\n        <p>Cover bald spots exactly where you need it — instant full coverage.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n      <div class=\"rizen-features__item\">\n        <span class=\"rizen-features__icon\">⛅<\/span>\n        <h3>WEATHER-PROOF CONFIDENCE<\/h3>\n        <p>Rain, wind, heat — stays locked in all day, no excuses.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  .rizen-features {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__title {\n    font-size: clamp(16px, 3vw, 26px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    text-align: center;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    margin: 0 0 48px 0;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 24px;\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__col {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 48px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__item {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    text-align: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__icon {\n    font-size: 36px;\n    line-height: 1;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__item h3 {\n    font-size: clamp(11px, 1.4vw, 14px);\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__item p {\n    font-size: clamp(11px, 1.2vw, 13px);\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__center {\n    width: clamp(180px, 30vw, 380px);\n  }\n\n  .rizen-features__center img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: auto;\n    display: block;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  }\n\n  \/* Mobile *\/\n  @media (max-width: 640px) {\n    .rizen-features__grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .rizen-features__center {\n      width: 220px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      order: -1;\n    }\n\n    .rizen-features__col {\n      gap: 32px;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"custom_liquid_CaymNK":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-title\">Frequently asked questions:<\/h2>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-list\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Will anyone be able to tell I'm using it?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>Practically invisible unless you mention it yourself. It merges naturally with your own hair, even under strong light or at close range. The finish replicates real hair thickness — no powdery residue, no artificial shine. In most cases, people won't realise you've applied anything at all.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is it suitable for every hair type?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>Yes, RIZEN™ Densify is designed to work with all hair textures, whether straight, wavy, curly, or Afro. It blends effortlessly with your natural look and stays secure, even on short or tightly coiled hair.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is it tricky or messy to apply?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>Not at all — simply use a small amount and apply with the built-in applicator. The process takes around 10 seconds, and once left to dry for 2–3 minutes, it leaves no residue or mess behind.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>Is it safe for a sensitive scalp?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>Yes — it's entirely safe. RIZEN™ Densify is dermatologist-approved and made with gentle, naturally-derived ingredients. Free from harsh chemicals, it's suitable for everyday use, even on delicate or easily irritated skin.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>What exactly goes into this formula?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>Only carefully selected ingredients: Talc, Mica, Silica, Magnesium Stearate, Squalane, Dimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexyl Glycerin, natural waxes, and Iron Oxides for colour. Free from alcohol, harsh chemicals, or irritants — every component is cosmetic-grade and safety-tested.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>If it's waterproof, how do I take it off?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>It comes out completely with a normal shampoo wash. Although resistant to rain and perspiration, it rinses away effortlessly during your usual hair-washing routine.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>How long will one container last me?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>On average, a single container lasts about 2–3 weeks with regular use. That's why we created our subscription offer — for just $39.97 you get 3 containers delivered every month, so you're never caught without coverage.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-trigger\" onclick=\"toggleFaq(this)\">\n        <span>What if it doesn't work for me?<\/span>\n        <svg class=\"faq-chevron\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n          <polyline points=\"6,9 12,15 18,9\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#111\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"\/>\n        <\/svg>\n      <\/button>\n      <div class=\"faq-content\">\n        <p>RIZEN™ Densify comes with a 30-day money-back guarantee — no questions asked. That said, with the majority of customers reordering, chances are you'll be looking for your next jar before the first one is even finished.<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n  .faq-section {\n    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n    background: #fff;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    max-width: 860px;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n\n  .faq-title {\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin: 0 0 40px 0;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n\n  .faq-list {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  .faq-item {\n    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n\n  .faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n\n  .faq-trigger {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    padding: 20px 0;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    gap: 16px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n\n  .faq-trigger span {\n    font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 16px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #111;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n  }\n\n  .faq-chevron {\n    width: 20px;\n    height: 20px;\n    min-width: 20px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n  }\n\n  .faq-trigger.open .faq-chevron {\n    transform: rotate(180deg);\n  }\n\n  .faq-content {\n    display: none;\n    padding: 0 24px 20px 0;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content.open {\n    display: block;\n  }\n\n  .faq-content p {\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.6vw, 15px);\n    color: #444;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n<\/style>\n\n<script>\n  function toggleFaq(btn) {\n    btn.classList.toggle('open');\n    const content = btn.nextElementSibling;\n    content.classList.toggle('open');\n  }\n<\/script>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"custom_liquid_UFbria":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<style>\n  .rizen-reviews {\n    background: #f9f9f9;\n    padding: 40px 16px;\n    width: 100%;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__stars-row {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__stars {\n    color: #f5a623;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__rating-text {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #333;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__title {\n    font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 32px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    margin: 0 0 28px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.01em;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__tabs {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 10px;\n    justify-content: center;\n    margin-bottom: 32px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__tab {\n    padding: 10px 20px;\n    border-radius: 50px;\n    border: 2px solid #ccc;\n    background: #fff;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #111;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: all 0.2s ease;\n    font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__tab:hover {\n    border-color: #111;\n    color: #111;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__tab.active {\n    background: #111;\n    border-color: #111;\n    color: #fff;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 24px;\n    max-width: 1000px;\n    margin: 0 auto 24px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-review-card {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n    padding: 0 16px;\n    border-right: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-review-card:last-child {\n    border-right: none;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-review-card__stars {\n    color: #f5a623;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-review-card__text {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-review-card__author {\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #111;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__dots {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__dot {\n    width: 8px;\n    height: 8px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #ccc;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: background 0.2s;\n  }\n\n  .rizen-reviews__dot.active {\n    background: #111;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 640px) {\n    .rizen-reviews__grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 20px;\n    }\n    .rizen-review-card {\n      border-right: none;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n      padding-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .rizen-review-card:last-child {\n      border-bottom: none;\n    }\n    .rizen-reviews__tab {\n      font-size: 12px;\n      padding: 8px 14px;\n    }\n  }\n<\/style>\n\n<div class=\"rizen-reviews\">\n\n  <div class=\"rizen-reviews__stars-row\">\n    <span class=\"rizen-reviews__stars\">★★★★★<\/span>\n    <span class=\"rizen-reviews__rating-text\">4.8 stars — 32,000+ men<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <h2 class=\"rizen-reviews__title\">What Men Are Saying About RIZEN™ Densify<\/h2>\n\n  <div class=\"rizen-reviews__tabs\">\n    <button class=\"rizen-reviews__tab active\" onclick=\"rizenSwitchTab('results', event)\">Results<\/button>\n    <button class=\"rizen-reviews__tab\" onclick=\"rizenSwitchTab('application', event)\">Application<\/button>\n    <button class=\"rizen-reviews__tab\" onclick=\"rizenSwitchTab('vs', event)\">vs. Other Products<\/button>\n    <button class=\"rizen-reviews__tab\" onclick=\"rizenSwitchTab('confidence', event)\">Confidence<\/button>\n    <button class=\"rizen-reviews__tab\" onclick=\"rizenSwitchTab('value', event)\">Value<\/button>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"rizen-reviews__grid\" id=\"rizen-reviews-grid\"><\/div>\n  <div class=\"rizen-reviews__dots\" id=\"rizen-reviews-dots\"><\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<script>\n  const rizenReviews = {\n    results: [\n      { text: \"I've been using it for 3 weeks and honestly can't believe how natural it looks. My barber didn't even notice until I told him.\", author: \"James T.\" },\n      { text: \"Bald spot on my crown is completely gone. Applied it before my sister's wedding and looked better than I have in years.\", author: \"Marcus D.\" },\n      { text: \"Used Toppik for 5 years. This is 10x better. Stays put for the whole work day, including my evening gym session.\", author: \"Andy Brown\" },\n      { text: \"Turned down so many events because I was embarrassed of my thinning crown. Used Rizen at a friend's wedding and actually enjoyed myself.\", author: \"Johnny Davis\" },\n      { text: \"Used to wear a hat everywhere, even indoors. Gave this a try and it really does work like magic.\", author: \"Brandon Jones\" },\n      { text: \"My hairline was really getting to me. This stuff gives me my confidence back every single morning in seconds.\", author: \"Ryan K.\" },\n    ],\n    application: [\n      { text: \"Takes literally 10 seconds. Tap it on, blend with fingers, done. No mess, no residue. Easiest grooming product I own.\", author: \"Steve M.\" },\n      { text: \"I was worried it would be complicated but it's the simplest thing. Dry hair, tap on, blend. That's it.\", author: \"Liam F.\" },\n      { text: \"The applicator is genius. No fallout on my clothes, no powdery mess. Clean and quick every time.\", author: \"Noah A.\" },\n      { text: \"I apply it in the car before meetings. 10 seconds max. Nobody has ever noticed I'm wearing it.\", author: \"Carlos R.\" },\n      { text: \"First time I used it I was shocked how easy it was. Expected a learning curve but there isn't one.\", author: \"Daniel P.\" },\n      { text: \"Application is foolproof. Even blends perfectly on my curly hair which I didn't expect.\", author: \"Jamal S.\" },\n    ],\n    vs: [\n      { text: \"I've tried every fiber spray on the market. RIZEN is the only one that survives a full gym workout without smudging.\", author: \"Tom B.\" },\n      { text: \"Compared to Toppik this stays on twice as long and looks twice as natural. Not even close.\", author: \"Will H.\" },\n      { text: \"Other brands leave a weird shine or powdery look. RIZEN actually looks like real hair. Huge difference.\", author: \"Chris N.\" },\n      { text: \"Tried 4 different brands before this. All of them transferred onto my pillow. RIZEN doesn't.\", author: \"Kevin O.\" },\n      { text: \"The waterproofing is what sets it apart. Got caught in rain wearing it and nothing moved. Incredible.\", author: \"Patrick L.\" },\n      { text: \"Generic fibers fall off when you sweat. RIZEN locks in. Game changer for anyone active.\", author: \"Tyler W.\" },\n    ],\n    confidence: [\n      { text: \"I walk into rooms differently now. Hard to explain but covering that spot changed something in me mentally.\", author: \"David M.\" },\n      { text: \"I stopped avoiding mirrors. That says everything about what this product did for my confidence.\", author: \"Omar S.\" },\n      { text: \"My wife said I seem happier lately. I didn't tell her about the product — she just noticed the change in me.\", author: \"Brett A.\" },\n      { text: \"I started going to the gym again because I stopped being self-conscious at the locker room.\", author: \"Victor L.\" },\n      { text: \"No more hat at the beach. I actually went swimming with family and didn't stress once.\", author: \"Jason T.\" },\n      { text: \"It sounds small but being able to run my hands through my hair without worry is a big deal to me.\", author: \"Eric C.\" },\n    ],\n    value: [\n      { text: \"For the price this is insane value. One jar lasted me almost a month and I use it daily.\", author: \"Sam B.\" },\n      { text: \"I spent more on a single bottle of Sauvage than this costs and this product actually changes my life.\", author: \"Nate G.\" },\n      { text: \"Compared to hair transplant consultations I was looking into, this is essentially free. And it works immediately.\", author: \"Frank D.\" },\n      { text: \"Reordered twice already. Great quality and the subscription price makes it even better.\", author: \"Jad R.\" },\n      { text: \"Best money I've spent on grooming in years. Delivers exactly what it promises.\", author: \"Alex V.\" },\n      { text: \"Bought it skeptically. Now I tell every guy I know about it. The value is unbeatable.\", author: \"Mark J.\" },\n    ],\n  };\n\n  let rizenCurrentTab = 'results';\n  let rizenCurrentPage = 0;\n  const rizenPerPage = 3;\n\n  function rizenSwitchTab(tab, event) {\n    rizenCurrentTab = tab;\n    rizenCurrentPage = 0;\n    document.querySelectorAll('.rizen-reviews__tab').forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));\n    event.target.classList.add('active');\n    rizenRenderReviews();\n  }\n\n  function rizenRenderReviews() {\n    const reviews = rizenReviews[rizenCurrentTab];\n    const totalPages = Math.ceil(reviews.length \/ rizenPerPage);\n    const start = rizenCurrentPage * rizenPerPage;\n    const visible = reviews.slice(start, start + rizenPerPage);\n\n    document.getElementById('rizen-reviews-grid').innerHTML = visible.map(r => `\n      <div class=\"rizen-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"rizen-review-card__stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n        <p class=\"rizen-review-card__text\">\"${r.text}\"<\/p>\n        <span class=\"rizen-review-card__author\">— ${r.author}<\/span>\n      <\/div>\n    `).join('');\n\n    document.getElementById('rizen-reviews-dots').innerHTML = Array.from({length: totalPages}, (_, i) => `\n      <div class=\"rizen-reviews__dot ${i === rizenCurrentPage ? 'active' : ''}\" onclick=\"rizenGoToPage(${i})\"><\/div>\n    `).join('');\n  }\n\n  function rizenGoToPage(page) {\n    rizenCurrentPage = page;\n    rizenRenderReviews();\n  }\n\n  rizenRenderReviews();\n<\/script>","full_width":false,"show_divider":false,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}}},"order":["empty-space","main","product-recommendations","scrolling_promotion_6Xj9FQ","image_with_text_bLaXbE","image_with_text_pTW7gg","custom_liquid_hkAJ9R","custom_liquid_CaymNK","custom_liquid_UFbria"]}